BP Desulfurization Unit Shut at Carson, California, Refinery

-- B y   A a r o n   C l a r k
-- 
2011-03-21T19:04:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/bp-desulfurization-unit-shut-at-carson-california-refinery.html
  BP Plc (BP/)  had a desulfurization unit
shut at its Carson, California, refinery March 19, according to
a person familiar with the plant’s operations.  The person didn’t know what caused the outage or how long
the unit might be offline.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Aaron Clark in New York at 
